{"tid":830294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無懼網路酸民！獨腳正妹勇奪義大利小姐選美季軍","createTime":"2018-09-21T05:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T02:12:25.000Z","uid":75969,"like":386,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"881f26d8f25f773566bec43311618cdaeff740f3","tid":830294,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180921/640_c7cec0c8edd365629faedbb5195f0b90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180921%2F640_c7cec0c8edd365629faedbb5195f0b90.jpg&h=40fe5eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">18歲佳麗博荻（Chiara Bordi）勇奪義大利小姐選美季軍！翻攝《Instagram》chiarabordi_</span><br />\n<br />\n本屆義大利小姐選美決賽，當地時間9月20日在米蘭舉行，左腳穿義肢的18歲佳麗博荻（Chiara Bordi）勇奪季軍！<br />\n <br />\n《Sputnik News》介紹，博荻（Chiara Bordi）雖然少了左小腿以下的部分，但熱愛溜冰、獨木舟、衝浪及攀岩等等戶外運動，未來的夢想是成為1位整形外科醫師！<br />\n <br />\n常常在《Instagram》chiarabordi_分享生活照的博荻，大方地展示其義肢，已經有超過5萬名粉絲追隨！<br />\n <br />\n介紹中說，博荻是在13歲時因騎單車出了嚴重車禍，不但住院長達9個月，還被切除了左小腿。當時博荻非常痛苦，甚至想結束生命，但在家人的安慰與支持下，才熬過傷痛，之後，姊姊還拿一些肢體殘缺的女模照片給博荻看，讓她燃起生命的火花，並決心向時裝界發展。<br />\n <br />\n介紹中說，博荻讀書時也一邊當模特兒，她回憶起首次走上伸展台的情形，雖然心裡很擔心，但由於觀眾對她微笑並熱烈鼓掌，讓她信心大增。<br />\n <br />\n在這次選美的決賽前夕，一些網路酸民取笑性般地預測說，她「會因缺少1條腿，獲得同情分數」，博荻則發文反擊說，自己是少了1條腿沒錯，但「你們卻少了良心與腦袋」。<br />\n <br />\n博荻現在為英國1間推動「時裝界多元」的模特兒公司工作，她表示，不能認同「傷殘是人生缺陷」的看法，而且自信地說：「我的美並不因義肢而減少。」<br />\n <br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180921/640_6615840b4b274baec5549caefb183e1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180921%2F640_6615840b4b274baec5549caefb183e1c.jpg&h=d1c1b29d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">博荻（Chiara Bordi）13歲的時候因單車事故失去左小腿。翻攝《Instagram》chiarabordi_<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180921/1433678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1433678&d=FSuEM9jv38mr8qdJ%2BqezmMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=dbbc1de2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1433678&h=27c2073c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180921/1433678</a>"},{"pid":"bbf37f52fb0e4af863b715bfc291aeebcadb04b5","tid":830294,"uid":5945,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42becc99d6527a3ed4f6ff3928e274bd81ac0c5e","tid":830294,"uid":53687,"like":859,"dislike":2,"score":857,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"咁佢其他部位真係靚，<br />\n點都好過班左膠選個唐氏樣出嚟。"},{"pid":"61639f82550028cec80d31bfc4351ac7722a0103","tid":830294,"uid":47112,"like":262,"dislike":1,"score":261,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"好鬼型 好cyberpunk"},{"pid":"37919b0c01c96b49d043b4dfb698a4630bad3714","tid":830294,"uid":1655,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"61639f82550028cec80d31bfc4351ac7722a0103","tid":830294,"uid":47112,"like":262,"dislike":1,"score":261,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"好鬼型 好cyberpunk"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"想俾佢踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14cf5435aeaa9e5d0f630ad2767eed9f475bef7","tid":830294,"uid":178800,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"樣靚已屈機"},{"pid":"7908f17a0e398f72da6f50572ada19e04a0921b9","tid":830294,"uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":309,"score":-306,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"冠軍Carlotta Maggiorana<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.donnaglamour.it/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/IM_Carlotta_Maggiorana.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna